OL,3,CA jump in bond yields: Bad news for
OL,4,Cmortgage holders, and for the
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,FAs of market-close today,
OL,8,Finternational investors were charging
OL,9,Fthe government an effective interest
OL,10,Frate of 4.8% to borrow over a 10-year
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FBack in July, when Labour won the
OL,14,Felection, what's called the "yield" on
OL,15,F10 year government bonds stood at 4.1%.
OL,17,FOn Budget Day (October 30), it stood
OL,18,Fat 4.3%. The UK is not alone.
OL,19,FInvestors have been offloading US,
OL,20,FFrench, German and Italian government
OL,21,Fdebt.
