OL,7,FLast October, the Office for Budget
OL,8,FResponsibility (OBR) calculated
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves was on track
OL,10,Fto deliver on her promise to balance
OL,11,Fthe current budget - the difference
OL,12,Fbetween the government's revenue and
OL,13,Fwhat it spends, excluding investment -
OL,14,Fby 2029/30 with #9.9 billion to spare.
