OL,4,Cmortgage holders, and for the
OL,5,CChancellor
OL,7,F"If bond yields remains at this level,
OL,8,Fit means that the chancellor will have
OL,9,Fto stand up in the commons on March 26
OL,10,Fand either admit she's broken her own
OL,11,Ffiscal rules or announce policies that
OL,12,Fwill trim government spending or
OL,13,Fincrease taxes,' said Paul Dale, chief
OL,14,Feconomist at Capital Economics.
OL,16,FIn a statement, a Treasury
OL,17,Fspokesperson said "no one should be in
OL,18,Fany doubt that meeting the fiscal
OL,19,Frules is non-negotiable".
